{"id":303363,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/bbc-印尼监狱逾百人越狱-警方称控制局势/","date":"2013-07-12T14:30:11Z","modified":"2013-07-12T14:30:11Z","title":"BBC | 印尼监狱逾百人越狱 警方称控制局势","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<p>视频：印尼监狱暴乱逾百犯人越狱</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/448x252/worldservice/assets/images/2013/07/12/130712115131_jailbreak_sumatra_indonesia_11jul2013_reuters_640x360_reuters_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"448\" height=\"252\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>在苏门答腊岛城市棉兰一座监狱发生暴乱，100多名犯人越狱。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwsodprogrf.bbc.co.uk%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fdps%2F2013%2F07%2Fsd_indon%2520sumatra_jail%25201244%252012%25207_105_1134693_16x9_hi.mp4\"><span>收看</span>mp4</a></p>\n<p>没有安装Flash播放器</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adobe.com%2Fproducts%2Fflashplayer%2F\">下载Flash</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fmultimedia%2F2013%2F07%2F130712_vid_sumatra_prison_riot.shtml%3Fbw%3Dbb%26amp%3Bmp%3Dwm%26amp%3Bbbcws%3D1%26amp%3Bnews%3D1\"><span>用视窗媒体播放器播放</span></a></p>\n</div>\n<p>印度尼西亚苏门答腊岛城市棉兰一座监狱发生骚乱。不过，印尼保安部在星期五（7月12日）表示，混乱已受到控制。</p>\n<p>在棉兰的Tanjung Gusta监狱的囚犯在星期四（11日）闹事，监狱一部分被焚烧，据报5人在暴乱中死亡，超过100名囚犯越狱，包括恐怖主义罪犯。</p>\n<p>印尼警方在星期五表示，他们已控制了混乱情况，抓回至少55名逃犯，大部分囚犯已经回到牢房。</p>\n<p>负责监狱事务的印尼官方发言人对法新社说，官员和一群囚犯代表会面。</p>\n<p>此前，警方说暴乱起因是停电导致供水中断引发的。</p>\n<p>发生暴乱的监狱原本只能容纳1000多人，但现在囚禁了2600多名犯人。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"326\" fram